---
// The universal query lifecycle (apps/baas/wiki/00-overview.md §3, simplified
// to 6 steps). The numbered circles match the <ol> rendered beside it.
---

<div class="gb-split">
	<ol class="gb-checklist" role="list">
		<li><strong>Call one API.</strong> Your app sends <span class="gb-mono">/query/v1/&lt;mount&gt;/tables/&lt;table&gt;</span> with an API key + JWT — same call for every engine.</li>
		<li><strong>Kong gates the edge.</strong> Key auth, JWT verification, per-IP rate limits, request IDs.</li>
		<li><strong>Rust applies your tier honestly.</strong> Capability mask (403 <span class="gb-mono">capability_gated</span>) and token bucket (429) — in 3.3 MiB, in-process.</li>
		<li><strong>Go resolves the mount.</strong> The adapter-registry decrypts your AES-256-GCM-stored DSN and returns the engine target.</li>
		<li><strong>The engine pool executes.</strong> Parameterised queries on a long-lived pool — 8 ms p50.</li>
		<li><strong>Changes fan out.</strong> Outbox CDC feeds webhooks and realtime WebSocket subscribers.</li>
	</ol>
	<figure>
		<svg class="gb-diagram" viewBox="0 0 720 252" role="img" aria-labelledby="dg-flow-title dg-flow-desc">
			<title id="dg-flow-title">Request flow through the planes</title>
			<desc id="dg-flow-desc">
				A request travels from the client to the Kong gateway, then to the Rust data plane, which asks
				the Go adapter-registry to resolve the encrypted mount, executes on the engine pools, and fans
				changes out to webhooks and realtime subscribers. Steps are numbered one to six, matching the
				adjacent list.
			</desc>
			<defs>
				<marker id="gb-arrow-flow" viewBox="0 0 8 8" refX="7" refY="4" markerWidth="7" markerHeight="7" orient="auto-start-reverse">
					<path d="M0 0L8 4L0 8z" fill="#7a8aa6" />
				</marker>
			</defs>

			<rect class="d-box" x="16" y="42" width="104" height="54" rx="10" />
			<text class="d-label" x="68" y="74" text-anchor="middle">client</text>
			<circle class="d-step" cx="68" cy="34" r="9" /><text class="d-step-num" x="68" y="37.5" text-anchor="middle">1</text>

			<path class="d-flow" d="M120 69h54" marker-end="url(#gb-arrow-flow)" />
			<rect class="d-box" x="176" y="42" width="120" height="54" rx="10" />
			<text class="d-label" x="236" y="68" text-anchor="middle">Kong</text>
			<text class="d-faint" x="236" y="84" text-anchor="middle">keys · JWT · limits</text>
			<circle class="d-step" cx="236" cy="34" r="9" /><text class="d-step-num" x="236" y="37.5" text-anchor="middle">2</text>

			<path class="d-flow d-flow--hot" d="M296 69h54" marker-end="url(#gb-arrow-flow)" />
			<rect class="d-box d-box--rust" x="352" y="42" width="150" height="54" rx="10" />
			<text class="d-label" x="427" y="68" text-anchor="middle">Rust data plane</text>
			<text class="d-faint" x="427" y="84" text-anchor="middle">mask · bucket · 3.3 MiB</text>
			<circle class="d-step" cx="427" cy="34" r="9" /><text class="d-step-num" x="427" y="37.5" text-anchor="middle">3</text>

			<path class="d-flow d-flow--hot" d="M502 69h54" marker-end="url(#gb-arrow-flow)" />
			<rect class="d-box d-box--accent" x="558" y="42" width="146" height="54" rx="10" />
			<text class="d-label" x="631" y="68" text-anchor="middle">engine pools</text>
			<text class="d-faint" x="631" y="84" text-anchor="middle">8 ms p50</text>
			<circle class="d-step" cx="631" cy="34" r="9" /><text class="d-step-num" x="631" y="37.5" text-anchor="middle">5</text>

			<path class="d-flow" d="M427 96v44" marker-end="url(#gb-arrow-flow)" />
			<rect class="d-box d-box--go" x="340" y="144" width="174" height="50" rx="10" />
			<text class="d-label" x="427" y="166" text-anchor="middle">adapter-registry (Go)</text>
			<text class="d-faint" x="427" y="182" text-anchor="middle">AES-256-GCM mounts</text>
			<circle class="d-step" cx="427" cy="136" r="9" /><text class="d-step-num" x="427" y="139.5" text-anchor="middle">4</text>

			<path class="d-flow" d="M631 96v44" marker-end="url(#gb-arrow-flow)" />
			<rect class="d-box" x="544" y="144" width="174" height="50" rx="10" />
			<text class="d-label" x="631" y="166" text-anchor="middle">outbox CDC</text>
			<text class="d-faint" x="631" y="182" text-anchor="middle">webhooks · realtime</text>
			<circle class="d-step" cx="631" cy="136" r="9" /><text class="d-step-num" x="631" y="139.5" text-anchor="middle">6</text>

			<text class="d-faint" x="16" y="232">engines: postgresql · mysql/mariadb · mongodb · sqlite · redis · cockroachdb · mssql · http</text>
		</svg>
	</figure>
</div>
